      <title>祖马要求南非最高法院停止议会开会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/zuma-asks-south-africa-s-top-court-to-stop-parliament-sitting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在立法者预定选举总统的三天前，前南非总统雅各布·祖马 (Jacob Zuma) 领导的政党要求宪法法院阻止议会召开。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/zuma-asks-south-africa-s-top-court-to-stop-parliament-sitting</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 09:19:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称内塔尼亚胡支持以色列与哈马斯战争停火计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/us-says-netanyahu-backs-cease-fire-plan-for-israel-hamas-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯表示，以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡在耶路撒冷举行的会议上重申了对停火提议的承诺，美国正试图为总统乔·拜登宣布的计划争取势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/us-says-netanyahu-backs-cease-fire-plan-for-israel-hamas-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 09:04:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯和巴西希望通过深化关系来吸引投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/saudi-arabia-brazil-hope-to-kindle-investment-with-deeper-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个是沙漠王国，正在逐渐摆脱对化石燃料的依赖。另一个是农业发达、矿产资源丰富的国家。沙特阿拉伯和巴西相距数千英里，但命运却让它们比以往任何时候都更加接近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/saudi-arabia-brazil-hope-to-kindle-investment-with-deeper-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度前煤炭部长肩负实现可再生能源目标的重任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/india-s-former-coal-minister-tasked-with-hitting-renewable-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[普拉拉德·乔希 (Pralhad Joshi) 被任命为可再生能源部长，他因将印度煤炭产量提升至创纪录水平而受到赞誉，其任务是加快推广太阳能和风能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/india-s-former-coal-minister-tasked-with-hitting-renewable-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 08:32:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
