    <item>
      <title>中国将自 2017 年以来首次派总理访问澳大利亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/china-to-send-premier-to-australia-for-first-time-in-seven-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[李强总理将于周六抵达澳大利亚，他将成为七年来访问澳大利亚的最高级别中国领导人，这一外交里程碑可能会因两国在投资和军事部署问题上再度出现的摩擦而黯然失色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/china-to-send-premier-to-australia-for-first-time-in-seven-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 06:07:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称四名教师遇刺事件不会影响中美关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/four-us-college-teachers-injured-in-china-park-stabbing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，美国一所大学的四名教师在公园散步时被刺伤的事件不应影响两国关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/four-us-college-teachers-injured-in-china-park-stabbing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 02:51:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲就维持俄乌天然气管道畅通进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/europe-in-talks-to-keep-russia-ukraine-gas-pipeline-flowing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲官员正在就如何维持俄罗斯-乌克兰一条重要管道的天然气输送进行谈判，以阻止莫斯科的战争进一步损害欧洲大陆的能源供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/europe-in-talks-to-keep-russia-ukraine-gas-pipeline-flowing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 17:42:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜为何向韩国发送装满垃圾的气球</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/why-north-korea-is-sending-trash-filled-balloons-into-south-korea-quicktake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜放飞了近 2,000 个载满垃圾的气球，军事高度集中的朝韩边境地区局势愈发紧张。作为回应，韩国恢复了旨在激怒平壤的首次扩音广播，几天后，朝鲜士兵短暂越过其领土并撤退，朝韩双方鸣枪警告。世界上军事化程度最高的边境之一的反复交锋引发了人们对意外升级并可能失控的担忧]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/why-north-korea-is-sending-trash-filled-balloons-into-south-korea-quicktake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 03:13:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
